ssets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n配件都玩死你</blockquote><br />\n公平啲，依家部機新出，又無向下相容，就算送game都無野可以送，唔通送新game咩<br />\n依家新人事新作風，先黎半年免費會藉試行，我覺得過多排應該會檢討個送game制度<br />\n<br />\n個柄有無得充電其實又唔係咁重要，應該無人會連續打廿個鐘都唔插返落部機啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2ab7b921d688ec0f7dc48286626effbd650e8a","tid":104593,"uid":6366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:03:42.000Z","msg":"繼續反就岩喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9da10eda4ceda791e869dc828c24eb53e37862c0","tid":104593,"uid":29738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:07:57.000Z","msg":"留名等睇 冇人玩"},{"pid":"4ece2cb853fc046bae3d0b4744f6fea42c5cf42a","tid":104593,"uid":53450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>直頭on9添啦<br />\n隔黎pan二月送 until dawn <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老任重係到on99咁<br />\n個抦重要係膠黎 無得充電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n配件都玩死你</blockquote><br />\n公平啲，依家部機新出，又無向下相容，就算送game都無野可以送，唔通送新game咩<br />\n依家新人事新作風，先黎半年免費會藉試行，我覺得過多排應該會檢討個送game制度<br />\n<br />\n個柄有無得充電其實又唔係咁重要，應該無人會連續打廿個鐘都唔插返落部機啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢依家先岀部機岀黎就預左同依家既情況比較 唔通一句新岀就可以叫人就一就先咩  又要等 咁買家咪等佢整好啲先買囉 <br />\n咁咪睇下到時咩情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有得直接充個手掣唔得 係要每次玩完左蚊右蚊 左插右插<br />\n想買 但啲細節位令我覺得佢好撚度縮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上wiiu既前科 我等年尾再決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f3de04cc61517a481d5c1d661553316187bed01","tid":104593,"uid":60432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T16:40:11.000Z","msg